patch:
diff --git a/Include/refcount.h b/Include/refcount.h
index 9a4e15065ec..4abcaedcaeb 100644
--- a/Include/refcount.h
+++ b/Include/refcount.h
@@ -501,10 +501,10 @@ static inline PyObject* _Py_XNewRef(PyObject *obj)
 // Names overridden with macros by static inline functions for best
 // performances.
 #if !defined(Py_LIMITED_API) || Py_LIMITED_API+0 < 0x030b0000
-#  define Py_NewRef(obj) _Py_NewRef(_PyObject_CAST(obj))
+#  define Py_NewRef(obj) _Py_XNewRef(_PyObject_CAST(obj))
 #  define Py_XNewRef(obj) _Py_XNewRef(_PyObject_CAST(obj))
 #else
-#  define Py_NewRef(obj) _Py_NewRef(obj)
+#  define Py_NewRef(obj) _Py_XNewRef(obj)
 #  define Py_XNewRef(obj) _Py_XNewRef(obj)
 #endif
 
@@ -512,4 +512,4 @@ static inline PyObject* _Py_XNewRef(PyObject *obj)
 #ifdef __cplusplus
 }
 #endif
-#endif   // !Py_REFCOUNT_H
+#endif   // !Py_REFCOUNT_H
\ No newline at end of file
